    </div>

    <div class="side">
      <h3>Why Attend?</h3>
      <p>This summit is designed to help you understand, experience, and apply AI in practical and exciting ways.</p>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles"></i></div>
        <div><strong>Live AI Demonstrations</strong><span>See powerful AI workflows in action.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-briefcase"></i></div>
        <div><strong>Career Opportunities</strong><span>Explore how AI is reshaping industries.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-network-wired"></i></div>
        <div><strong>Networking</strong><span>Meet professionals, founders, and creators.</span></div>
      </div>

      <!-- PAYMENT -->
      <div class="payment-wrap" id="paymentWrap">
        <div class="payment-card">
          <div id="paymentForm">
            <h2>Secure Your Seat</h2>
            <p>Your details are confirmed. Complete payment to lock in your spot.</p>

            <!-- Read-only summary of what was collected in chat -->
            <div class="summary-box">
              <p>Name &nbsp;<span id="summaryName"></span></p>
              <p>Email &nbsp;<span id="summaryEmail"></span></p>
              <p>Phone &nbsp;<span id="summaryPhone"></span></p>
            </div>

            <div class="input-group">
              <label>Registration Fee</label>
              <input type="text" value="GHS 500.00" readonly />
            </div>

            <div class="pay-error" id="payError"></div>

            <button class="pay-btn" id="payBtn" onclick="launchPaystack()">
              <span id="payBtnText">Pay GHS 500.00</span>
              <div class="pay-spinner" id="paySpinner"></div>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right" id="payBtnIcon"></i>
            </button>

            <div class="pay-secure">
